Maintainer: Tan Nguyen <tan@draftright.app>
Homepage: https://draftright.app
Description: AI-powered text rewriting tool
 DraftRight lets you select text anywhere on your desktop, pick a tone,
 and get a polished rewrite instantly. Supports professional, casual,
 friendly, concise, formal, and translation modes.
 .
 Press a global hotkey to capture your selection, choose a tone from
 the floating panel, and replace or copy the result.
